description.description_en: Rhizome about 1 cm in diameter.Fronds fan-shaped, cut into 2 halves, main lobes of each half narrowly lanceolate, with 2 main veins in each lobe, divided over 3/4 of way to base, apices acuminate, margins thickened with coarse serratiion; main veins prominently raised; young fronds densely covered with soft reddish-brown tomentum, especially on apices of lobes, mature fronds glabrous and glaucous beneath.
